title: His Own Worst Enemy: The Rise and Fall of Jon Jones  | Part 2

media:group.media:title: His Own Worst Enemy: The Rise and Fall of Jon Jones  | Part 2
media:group.media:description:
In this part of the Jon Jones series, we discuss Jon's battle with silver tongued pizza salesman, Chael Sonnen, his hall of fame war with Alexander Gustafsson, brutal beating of Glover Teixeira and the first part of his legendary feud with Daniel "Matt Serra" Cormier.
